{"type":null,"faqId":44308,"title":"邮箱设置","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">添加Email帐户 </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">进入电子邮件。登陆账号分为手动设置和自动设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">手动设置：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 账户设置界面，输入账号和密码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 点击手动设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 点击POP3，进入接收服务器设置界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4. 点击下一步，进入外发服务器设置界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5. 点击下一步，进入邮件接收设置界面，可选择收件箱检查频率。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">6. 点击下一步，进入设置电子邮件界面为此账户创建名称和您的姓名。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">7. 点击下一步，完成登录并进入收件箱界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">自动设置（自动设置需要手机中预置该类型Email的参数）：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 账户设置界面，输入账号和密码。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 点击下一步。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 点击下一步，进入邮件接收设置界面可选择收件箱检查频率。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4. 点击下一步，进入设置电子邮件界面为此账户创建名称和您的姓名。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5. 点击下一步，完成登录并进入收件箱界面。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">对于未预置的Email账户，登录过程中的设置，您可以登录电子邮件服务供应商的网站进行查询。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":2,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9808","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400456000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":25,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"邮箱,设置","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}